title: Ambi Skincare Even & Clear Exfoliating Wash, 5 Ounce
description: This unique cleanser with microbeads gently exfoliates skin by removing dead skin cells. It is specially formulated with a dermatologist-recommended skin clearing ingredient, salicylic acid and EvenBlend, a combination of soy extract and Vitamins C & E to help clear and prevent breakouts while keeping skin even-toned. With daily use, this creamy exfoliating cleanser rejuvenates skin, leaving it more radiant and smooth. It's gentle enough for sensitive skin, has a fresh scent, and rinses clean.
